{"article_id":"K4HFkI634o3RNJL9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump speaks to reporters","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"before boarding Air Force One at Morristown Municipal Airport in Morristown , N.J. , August 15 , 2019 .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"( Jonathan Ernst/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":3,"text":"President Trump said Monday","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that peace negotiations with the Taliban are \" dead","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"as far as I ' m concerned \"","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"after the terrorist group claimed responsibility for a bombing in Afghanistan","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that killed an American service member .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Trump called off a secret meeting with Taliban leaders and representatives of the Afghanistan government ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"which had been planned for Sunday at Camp David ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"after the Taliban claimed","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"its members carried out a suicide bombing in Kabul","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that killed twelve people ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"including a U.S. soldier .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Critics had called the plan","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"to meet for peace negotiations days before the 18th anniversary of the 9/11 terrorist attacks","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"disrespectful .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"\" It was my idea , \"","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"the president told reporters","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"about canceling the meeting .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"\" I didn ' t discuss it with anybody else .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"When I heard . . .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that they killed one of our soldiers and 12 other innocent people ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"there ' s no way","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"I ' m meeting . \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Trump further claimed","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that reports","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"that he had overruled advisers ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"including national- security adviser John Bolton and the vice president ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"to schedule the meeting in the first place","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"are false .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"A lot of Fake News is being reported","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that I overruled the VP and various advisers on a potential Camp David meeting with the Taliban .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"This Story is False !","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"I always think","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"it is good to meet","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"and talk ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"but in this case I decided not to .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"The Dishonest Media likes to create...","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"September 9 , 2019","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Trump also criticized the prolonged U.S. presence in Afghanistan ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"recalling his promise","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"to bring home the approximately 14,000 American troops","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"currently stationed in the war-torn country .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"We have been serving as policemen in Afghanistan ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"and that was not meant to be the job of our Great Soldiers , the finest on earth .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Over the last four days , we have been hitting our Enemy harder than at any time in the last ten years !","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"September 9 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"\" We ' re going to walk away from a deal","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"if others try to use violence","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"to achieve better ends in the negotiations , \"","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo said Sunday of the canceled meeting .","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"\" It ' s not right .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"It ' s not appropriate .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"It killed an American .","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"And it made no sense for the Taliban to be rewarded for that kind of bad behavior . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":119,"left":62,"right":118,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":62,"left":61,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":61,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":110,"right":117,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":66,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":3,"right":63,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":63,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":82,"right":108,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":71,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":67,"right":70,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":10,"right":69,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":11,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":73,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":76,"right":79,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":75,"right":20,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":17,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity"